data.description: Don't miss out on this spacious 3 bedroom colonial in South Western School District!  The home offers ample room for comfortable living  with a large kitchen, formal living and dining room, family room, primary suite, 2 full and 2 half baths,  and a finished lower level rec room with a wet bar.  You will also find ample storage space in the attic and unfinished basement area.  Outside, enjoy the tranquility of a fenced yard with a deck, perfect for entertaining or relaxing and enjoying nature's beauty that holds true to the address with frequently visiting cardinals.   Make this home yours before spring and take in the stunning magenta-colored blooms of the magnolia tree, visible from the dining room window or deck. The location can't be beat near shopping and restaurants and a convenient commute to Maryland.  It won't last long so schedule your visit now!
